left:46.8000pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;修补已渗漏构筑物，先用快速堵漏剂封堵，再用掺LFS抗裂防水剂的砂浆抹面。</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><strong>注意事项</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:46.8000pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;LFS在贮存及运输时，要防止淋雨、受潮，并在干燥处存放。</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:46.8000pt;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;LFS保质期为180天，超过保质期后应重新检验，合格仍可继续使用。</span></p>\r\n<table style="width:520px;">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="width:87px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:114px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">8小时</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">24小时</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">48小时</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="width:87px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">HSCA-Ⅰ</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:114px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">35&plusmn;5</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&ge;30</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&ge;55</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&ge;80</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="width:87px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">HSCA-Ⅱ</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:114px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">25&plusmn;5</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:106px;">\r\n				<p ali