n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:120px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&ge;70.0</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:72px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&ge;75.0</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:72px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&ge;80.0</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:72px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&ge;80.0</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="width:108px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">竖向膨胀率 %（MPa）</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:168px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">1d</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:120px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&ge;0.020</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:72px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&ge;0.020</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:72px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&ge;0.020</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:72px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&ge;0.020</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="width:276px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">钢筋握裹强度（圆钢） MPa&nbsp;&nbsp;28d</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:120px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&ge;4.0</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:72px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&ge;6.0</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:72px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&ge;6.0</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:72px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">&ge;6.0</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan="3" style="width:396px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">对钢筋锈蚀作用：应说明对钢筋有无锈蚀作用</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="3" style="width:216px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">对钢筋无锈蚀作用</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><strong>UGM</strong><strong>常见用途示例</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt="" src="/building/Public/upload/news/images/20160416081118.png" style="width: 183px; height: 96px; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;" /><img alt="" src="/building/Public/upload/news/images/20160416081138.png" style="width: 110px; height: 95px; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;" /><img alt="" src="/building/Public/upload/news/images/20160416081152.png" style="width: 102px; height: 96px; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;" /><img alt="" src="/building/Public/upload/news/images/20160416081214.png" style="width: 82px; height: 96px; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;" /></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;轨道与基础的连接 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;结构梁、柱的加固 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 灌浆补缝 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 轨道与基础的连接</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><strong>UGM</strong><strong>使用方法</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 参照冶金部颁布的《水泥基灌浆材料应用技术规范》GB/T50448，具体施工方法如下：</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="margin-left: 40px;">\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;UGM的施工温度规定为-5～40℃，适用温度规定为-10～60℃。</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style="margin-left: 40px;">\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;对于厚度50～150的小空间二次填补灌注，可直接用UGM加水拌合成灌浆材料，加水量为UGM的15%左右。</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style="margin-left: 40px;">\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;对于厚度大于150mm大空间的二次填补灌注，可加入5～10mm粒径的石子，石子的加入量为石子﹕UGM＝0.3﹕1，加入量为UGM的20%左右。</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style="margin-left: 40px;">\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;灌注前，要把填充空间清理干净，填充空间表面混凝土需预湿12小时。</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style="margin-left: 40px;">\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;按配合比拌制成灌浆料，可用机械或人工搅拌，但需用力拌合均匀。施工温度高时，可增加少量水拌至所需流动度。</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style="margin-left: 40px;">\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;灌注孔或小位空间时，可自流填充密实，灌注机器底座或杯口时，分层自流填满，并用薄片插捣，一定要把气体赶跑，灌注密实，稍干后，把外露面抹平压光。</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style="margin-left: 40px;">\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;灌注完后，经12小时便要浇水养护或用湿草袋覆盖养护，养护期7～14天。</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style="margin-left: 40px;">\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;UGM的干容重为2100kg/m<sup>3</sup>，即每1m<sup>3</sup>空间需2.1吨UGM干料。</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt="" src="/building/Public/upload/news/images/20160416081941.png" style="width: 312px; height: 113px;margin:0 auto;display:block;" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">1.自重灌浆法</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><img alt="" src="/building/Public/upload/news/images/20160416082227.png" style="width: 169px; height: 138px;" />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt="" src="/building/Public/upload/news/images/20160416082245.png" style="width: 144px; height: 141px;" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">2.高位漏斗灌浆法</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><img alt="" src="/building/Public/upload/news/images/20160416082332.png" style="width: 202px; height: 111px;" />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt="" src="/building/Public/upload/news/images/20160416082348.png" style="width: 137px; height: 140px;" /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">3.压力灌浆法</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><strong>UGM</strong><strong>注意事项</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="margin-left: 39pt;">\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style="font-size:14px;">UGM在贮存及运输时，要防止淋雨、受潮，并在干燥处存放。</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style="margin-left: 39pt;">\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style="font-size:14px;">UGM保质期为180天。</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><strong>UGM</strong><strong>产品监测</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 由中国建筑材料科学研究总院监制。委托国家建筑材料测试中心测试。</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><strong>UGM</strong><strong>产品包装</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 每包凈重25kg、50kg，有三层纸袋包装，内衬防潮胶膜。</span></p>\r\n', 0, '', 0, 1),
(36, 0, 7, '预应力孔道压浆料/剂（PSG / PSA）', '超级管理员', 1460795200, 1460795698, '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><strong>简介 </strong></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 在后张法预应力施工中，如何使管道压浆密实、不分层、强度均匀，钢铰线不锈蚀、预应力不损失，是近年来桥梁等结构工程安全使用100年以上必须考虑的问题。在我国众多桥梁中，因压浆质量问题造成管内钢绞线严重腐蚀已经为数不少，甚至个别桥梁发生倒塌事件。因此，提高我国后张法预应力管道灌浆材料的质量确保预应力桥梁的安全使用，已引起业界的高度重视。</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 预应力管道压浆料/剂（Grouts for Pre-stressed Structure / Grouting admixture）是本公司结合预应力管道压浆施工技术特点，研究、开发的一种专用于预应力管道压浆施工的灌浆料。该产品以钙矾石 (C<sub>3</sub>A&middot;3CaSO<sub>4</sub>&middot;32H<sub>2</sub>O) 结晶体为膨胀源，并辅以无机和有机组分，具有泌水率小、早强、微膨胀、稠度稳定、压浆饱满、粘结力强、提高钢铰线抗锈蚀性等，是保证预应力桥梁安全的水泥基灌浆材料。</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><strong>产品分类</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>预应力</strong><strong>管道压</strong><strong>浆料（</strong>PSG<strong>）</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 是本公司结合预应力管道压浆施工技术特点，研究、开发的一种专用于预应力管道压浆施工的水泥基压浆材料。现场只需加水搅拌即可使用。预应力管道压浆料减少了现场复配水泥等施工工序，尤其是避免了压浆剂与不同水泥间的适应性所产生的问题。适用于后张法预应力管道等其他需要高流动性的小缝隙粘结与填充灌浆。</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>预应力</strong><strong>管道压</strong><strong>浆剂（</strong>PSA<strong>）</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 压浆剂以 10% 左右掺入普通水泥可拌制成微膨胀灌浆材料，与普通水泥灌浆料相比，具有流动性好，不泌水、不分层、压浆饱满、早强、微膨胀等特性，并可一次性压浆施工，管道内浆体密实无孔隙，预应力钢筋不锈蚀，与混凝土粘结牢固。使用PSA之前应进行适应性试验，确保PSA与水泥之间有良好的适应性。</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;"><strong>技术指标</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 产品性能符合中华人民共和国标准《预应力孔道灌浆剂》（GB/T 25182-2010）以及《铁路后张法预应力混凝土梁管道压浆技术条件》（TB/T 3192-2008）、《公路桥涵施工技术规范》（JTG/T F50-2011）并付测试结果：</span></p>\r\n<table style="width:573px;">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan="4" style="width:177px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n					<span style="font-size:14px;">检验项目</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width:50px;">\r\n				<p align="center">\r\n		